android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.ACCESS_WIFI_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the information about the status of Wi-Fi.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.USE_FINGERPRINT.description: This constant was deprecated in API level 28. Applications should request USE_BIOMETRIC instead

manifest_analysis.desc: A Broadcast Receiver is found to be shared with other apps on the device therefore leaving it accessible to any other application on the device. It is protected by a permission which is not defined in the analysed application. As a result, the protection level of the permission should be checked where it is defined. If it is set to normal or dangerous, a malicious application can request and obtain the permission and interact with the component. If it is set to signature, only applications signed with the same certificate can obtain the permission.

"more_donation_tip_message4" : "1. Zuverlässig. Totalcoin ist ein grosses System, eine ausgewogene Mischung von effektiven Produkten. Wir haben mehrere schon implementierten Funktionen und noch vieler glänzenden Ideen. Totalcoin.me ist ein neuer und wichtiger Teil der Totalcoin-Umgebung.

playstore_details.title: Bitcoin Wallet Totalcoin - Buy and Sell Bitcoin
playstore_details.description:
Do you need a secure BTC or Ethereum wallet? Do you need to profitably buy Bitcoin instantly or sell it? With the help of our crypto wallet app for Android you will be able to send and receive any crypto currency anywhere in the world.
 
Try our p2p exchange! Localbitcoins is in your pocket. No need to use VPN, or suffer from delays and restrictions

Your Bitcoin, Ethereum and Bitcoin Cash are securely hidden in your blockchain wallet and always under your control.

Similar to paxful app here you can purcase Bitcoin using iTunes and Amazon gift cards, Western Union and MoneyGram.
 
MAIN FEATURES:
✓ Buy and sell crypto currency instantly using a free Bitcoin wallet
✓ Built-in p2p exchange. Trade with real and proven people, similar to Localbitcoins.
✓ Buy Bitcoin with debit card or with credit card (soon).
✓ Exchange BTC for Ethereum or Bitcoin Cash.
✓ Keep track of your cryptocurrency : Our app helps you see crypto prices and the value of your assets at any time.
✓ No fees for deposits and free withdrawals. Moreover, we calculate the optimal transaction fee for blockchain transactions by using the data over the past hour, but you can choose a fee amount on your own.
✓ Transfer cryptocurrency by a phone number.
✓ Secure transfer crypto currency by a phone number.
✓ Additional security of your cryptocurrency wallet: SMS authentication, Google 2-Step Verification, and fingerprint security.
✓ Buy and sell Bitcoin anonymously, using a phone number for authorization.
✓ Detailed transaction history of your Bitcoin wallet.
 
EASY TO USE:
☑ Beautiful, convenient, and ultrafast interface of a blockchain wallet.
☑ The possibility to securely store all your crypto currency investments in one place, quickly exchange Bitcoin or withdraw them.
☑ More than 30 currencies: US dollar (USD), euro (EUR), pound sterling (GBP), ruble (RUB), and others.
☑ Create your BTC, Ethereum wallet and Ripple wallet store everything in one place. Soon we will add more cryptocurrencies.
☑ Integration with our Telegram bot.
 
MULTI CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET SUPPORTS:
■ Bitcoin ( BTC )
■ Ethereum ( ETH )
■ Litecoin ( LTC )
■ Dash
■ Monero ( XMR )
■ USD Coin ( USDC )
■ Ripple ( XRP )
■ Dogecoin ( DOGE )
■ ZCash ( ZEC )
■ Ethereum Classic ( ETC )
■ Stellar ( XLM )
■ Tether ( USDT )
■ Tron ( TRX )
■ IOTA
■ Stallar ( XLM )
■ Cardano ( ADA )

TO BE ADDED SOON:
■ Gram ( Telegam-TON ) 
■ Tokens ERC20.
 
Totalcoin is a secure blockchain wallet for BTC, Ethereum, Bitcoin Cash and other cryptocurrencies, a universal android app to work in the cryptocurrency industry.
 
How to store and buy cryptocurrency? It is simple. Totalcoin.

OFFICIAL SITE:
Totalcoin
